{"tid":1007810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"促罰違法官吏　網民聯署進諫被拘捕","createTime":"2019-02-04T04:48:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T05:53:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"614c649da3cec905862014a5db61643ebcd1ba01","tid":1007810,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T04:48:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190204/20606004\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190204%2F20606004&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=98a747b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190204%2F20606004&h=c18d853a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190204/20606004</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年02月04日 <br />\n<br />\n促罰違法官吏　網民聯署進諫被拘捕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190204/large/04cf90p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190204%2Flarge%2F04cf90p.jpg&h=3ecf7649&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在中共嚴密管治下，網民進諫也被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地網傳251位北京市民簽署的《北京人向全國人大諫言書》，針對中共基層官員在執行政策過程中走樣變調，表示深惡痛絕，呼籲當局維穩要從懲違法官吏做起。據報道，中共當局已開始調查諫言書的簽名者，已定性是「反社會主義」事件。發起人已被公安帶走。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被指「反社會」<br />\n<br />\n該諫言書是251名北京公民和維權人士，利用市政府一個網上平台簽署的。內容包括要求公務員履行職責時，須主動公開姓名、職務；在固定地辦公須有明示牌以利公民監督。省、市、區、縣、鄉長每年定期定額接待上訪者，並作合法、合理有效處理。諫言書還要求尊重保護上訪人的權利不被侵犯；「維穩要從嚴懲各部門違法官吏入手」。諫言書還要求從首都北京做起，「清查滯留在京的截訪人，嚴厲打擊截訪、攔訪人，追究截訪人屬地政府第一責任人的責任。」<br />\n<br />\n活動發起人叫劉靜儒，2月1日已被北京公安帶走，目前尚未回家。與此同時，當局正在找與這次行動有關的主要人員，尋找群主，而且似乎已將事件定性為「反社會主義」。胡秀蘭是簽名者之一，她告訴外媒，公安已找她問是否簽名了、是甚麼意思，「我說，我就是維護我的權利。犯法不犯法？他說不犯法。」另一簽署人李慧琴透露「都逮好幾個人了」，稱「法院太壞了。習主席是好的，關鍵是底下的人壞。上面有政策，下面有對策。」<br />\n<br />\n美國之音  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n稱處境不安全　周永康媳婦再轟中共<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n全球迎豬年　 新年外遊首選泰國香港　 700萬人出國撒幣"},{"pid":"637addf036cce4ed3288ebb7ff80c6a7b134a762","tid":1007810,"uid":63482,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T04:54:53.000Z","msg":"<em>「法院太壞了。習主席是好的，關鍵是底下的人壞。上面有政策，下面有對策。」<br />\n</em><br />\n真心膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59485b6b12c91003ee80b49aacac3371f4d82084","tid":1007810,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"637addf036cce4ed3288ebb7ff80c6a7b134a762","tid":1007810,"uid":63482,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T04:54:53.000Z","msg":"<em>「法院太壞了。習主席是好的，關鍵是底下的人壞。上面有政策，下面有對策。」<br />\n</em><br />\n真心膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T05:22:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc37f157c716283a1b42498d26da6e21ccfcd922","tid":1007810,"uid":76455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"637addf036cce4ed3288ebb7ff80c6a7b134a762","tid":1007810,"uid":63482,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T04:54:53.000Z","msg":"<em>「法院太壞了。習主席是好的，關鍵是底下的人壞。上面有政策，下面有對策。」<br />\n</em><br />\n真心膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <i